header.name: Talairach
header.description: Modification of Standard Talairach labels originally from the Talairach Daemon package at www.talairach.org -- added several areas from the Juelich atlas (hippocampal subregions, major visual areas) plus some specific subcortical areas of interest. Original is a conversion of the Talairach structural labellings, kindly provided by Jack Lancaster and Diana Tordesillas GutiÃ©rrez at the Research Imaging Center, UTHSCSA, Texas. This is a digitised version of the original (coarsely sliced) Talairach atlas (Lancaster 2000) after the application of a correcting affine transform (Lancaster 2007) to register it into MNI152 space.
